token.welcome-message: This is a small family breeding kennel that specializes in breeding small german spitz (23 - 28 cm) in orange, orange-sable, créme, and créme-sable colors since 2008. The founders of the kennel were CH. Hakim Kaveta Bohemia, an orange male dog, and CH. Gina Orlovská perla, an orange female dog. We live in the Czech Republic, in an astonishing region of millstone grit rocks in the protected landscape area Broumovsko.
token.puppies-introduction-g: In the name-day of son Lukas, 18.10.2017, our female dog Ellis Esma Fox River gave birth to 4 girls and 1 boy. The father of the puppies is a charming CH. Jack Sandiré.
